{
  "type": "adapter_action",
  "id": "balancer/v2/vault-join-pool@1.0.0",
  "publisher": "balancer.eth",
  "schema_version": "3",
  "_note": "Balancer V2 Vault.joinPool(bytes32 poolId, address sender, address recipient, (address[] assets, uint256[] maxAmountsIn, bytes userData, bool fromInternalBalance) request) — selector 0xb95cac28. Source: balancer/balancer-v2-monorepo pkg/interfaces/contracts/vault/IVault.sol. Maps to Amm::AddLiquidity::Pooled. The pooled token set is the two index-aligned calldata arrays request.assets[] (token addrs) and request.maxAmountsIn[] (per-token max spend the user signs); zipped by $fn balancer_zip_token_amounts because the flat $args grammar cannot build a Vec<(TokenRef,U256)> from two arrays. min_lp_out (minBPTAmountOut) lives inside the opaque request.userData enum-tagged blob, extracted by $fn balancer_v2_userdata_field (JoinKind table); undecodable kinds fall back to 0 (conservative floor). pool_id is the bytes32 poolId directly (venue carries it; no slice needed). Vault 0xBA12222222228d8Ba445958a75a0704d566BF2C8 is identical on all chains; mainnet only here (multichain expansion deferred per scope contract).",
  "match": {
    "selector": "0xb95cac28",
    "chain_to_addresses": {
      "1": ["0xBA12222222228d8Ba445958a75a0704d566BF2C8"]
    }
  },
  "abi_fragment": {
    "function_name": "joinPool",
    "abi": {
      "name": "joinPool",
      "type": "function",
      "stateMutability": "payable",
      "inputs": [
        { "name": "poolId",    "type": "bytes32" },
        { "name": "sender",    "type": "address" },
        { "name": "recipient", "type": "address" },
        {
          "name": "request",
          "type": "tuple",
          "components": [
            { "name": "assets",              "type": "address[]" },
            { "name": "maxAmountsIn",        "type": "uint256[]" },
            { "name": "userData",            "type": "bytes"     },
            { "name": "fromInternalBalance", "type": "bool"      }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "outputs": []
    }
  },
  "emit": {
    "strategy": "single_emit",
    "body": {
      "domain": "amm",
      "amm": {
        "action": "add_liquidity",
        "add_liquidity": {
          "venue": {
            "name":      "balancer_v2",
            "chain":     "$chain",
            "vault":     "$to",
            "pool_id":   "$args.poolId",
            "pool_type": "weighted"
          },
          "params": {
            "kind": "pooled",
            "tokens": {
              "$fn": "balancer_zip_token_amounts",
              "$args": ["$chain", "$args.request[0]", "$args.request[1]"]
            },
            "min_lp_out": {
              "$fn": "balancer_v2_userdata_field",
              "$args": ["$args.request[2]", "join", "min_bpt"]
            },
            "recipient": "$args.recipient"
          },
          "live_inputs": {
            "pool_state": {
              "source": {
                "kind":       "onchain_view",
                "chain":      "$chain",
                "contract":   "$to",
                "function":   "getPoolTokens(bytes32)",
                "decoder_id": "balancer_v2_pool_tokens"
              },
              "ttl_s": 12
            },
            "current_price": {
              "source": {
                "kind":    "derived_from",
                "inputs":  [],
                "calc_id": "balancer_v2_pool_price"
              },
              "ttl_s": 12
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "requires": {
    "imperative": [],
    "adapter_capabilities": ["token_metadata"],
    "host_capabilities": [],
    "extension": ">=0.1.0"
  }
}
